LOREM KISMI: We are capable of doing any preventative and Corrective Maintenance / Her türlü kompleks elektronik sistemlerin önleyici ve düzeltici bakım onarımı yapılabilmektedir.
- Sed amet aliquam: (Bckg photo: Fener)
We have more than 5 years of experience on maintenance of Abovewater and Underwater Surveillance Systems
Our capability covers:
-Passive Sonar System
-Active Sonar System
-Diver Detection Sonar System
- Conductivity Temperature and Depth Sensors(CTD)
-Sonar Signal Processing Cabinets
- Electro-Optics Systems (Thermal, Color, Low-light TV cameras, Laser Range Finder, Pan-Tilt)
- Radar systems
- Consoles and Multi-Sensor Integration Software
